    "We collected data from 21 sources originating from various regions: USA (4), India (4), Canada (3), Australia (1), UK (1), New Zealand (1), and other global sources (7), aiming to avoid geographic and cultural biases (detailed in Tables [15, 16, 17] of the Appendix).",
    "Data Quantity Our KidLM corpus contains over 286,000 documents, approximately 2.91 million sentences, and 50.43 million words.",
